data.description: What an incredible opportunity! Large 4 bedroom ranch home, just minutes off Hwy 78, conveniently located close to shopping and dining. This home is loaded with potential, but there is some work to be done. There is a lot of square footage, bonus area converted to apartment, with 2nd kitchen area, back porch converted to sunroom, outbuilding, newer HVAC and roof.
